<plot>Sergeant John "Mac" MacPherson, of the Royal Canadian Mounted Police, is heading toward to a small Canadian Northwest settlement to investigate a series of crimes. Working undercover, using an assumed name, he prevents trouble between a white man and an Indian and, finally, after seeking refuge from the Indian tribe, is able to arrest the white men behind the trouble.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?653985</url></doc>
